snippet.title: Bel & Poppy 2019 | Updated Gameplay
snippet.description:
A game about a little ninja and her sleepy pistol. Now even purdier!

Originally created for A Game By It's Cover (AGBICjam) 2018, based on a Famicase design by Kristian Spears. Play for free: https://ramifactor.itch.io/bel-poppy

AGBICjam 2018: https://itch.io/jam/a-game-by-its-cover-2018

Famicase design: https://famicase.com/18/softs/249

Music:
Azureflux - Superbyte
Ramifactor - Let's Go Poppy
RoccoW - Bleeps Galore
